the dollar up from 16635 marks on friday 
the stock market in frankfurt on monday also reacted favorably 
to the first business day of economic union and the german stock 
index climbed to 191258 from 187990 on friday 
dealers remained optimistic that the west german stock market 
could be set for a continued rising trend if the economic union 
progesses smoothly to keep the inflation rate down 
although markets were steady to improved one dealer cautioned 
