nationalization of the partys property 
attacks on gorbachevs leadership are increasingly frequent as 
reformers and traditionalists find fault with a failing economy 
republics bent on secession and rampant crime 
i think we can return to this proposal the soviet leader 
said evenly in response to bludov and the congress overwhelmingly 
supported him 
