been late or mistaken in making key decisions but he laid much of 
the blame for the nations economic political and ecological 
crisis on a heavy legacy of abuse and stagnation under stalin 
and other leaders 
reformminded delegates said they were unimpressed with 
gorbachevs report 
i expected it to be more constructive more radical with 
