against which wheeler sings in a detached passionless way 
the best of the collection is heres where the story ends 
in which wheeler recalls a broken romance while handling that 
little souvenir of a terrible year at one point she sings the 
only thing i ever really wanted to say was wrong 
the line is piercing but its not enough to recommend this 
record 
by david dishneau associated press writer 
