the song back in 197576 that craze was sweeping the country 
the jargon was colorful and the american public liked that too 
it was laced with humor but it had a rebellious feeling about 
it and people responded to it 
we took a slice out of this lifestyle and talk and put it into 
a number it was just phenomenal you turned on the radio and in 
