when we are all here 
he doesnt plan to have a convoy touring the nation to plug the 
new album i might do a few promotional things but they had 
better come here to do the talk shows i have an aversion to going 
to hot cities 
i have a great love affair with this little town a town lost 
in time were not out to make a killing selling records this was 
a project of joy and to satisfy the loyal fans we did it as a 
creative outlet 
mccall a native of audubon iowa still has a cb radio in his 
fourwheel drive vehicle and continues to use the handle rubber 
duck but the cb radio craze is not what it once was 
we hardly ever use it he said its gathering dust we do 
